Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.55,0:01:50.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,[莉希安萨斯篇 前篇]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.55,0:01:56.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅雨季节真是有趣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.77,0:02:00.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像这样在天气变热之前先补充水分
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.29,0:02:03.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人界的自然真是好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.28,0:02:06.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 也不用这么激动吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.47,0:02:10.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我倒是很喜欢 撑着伞走路
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.02,0:02:13.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不觉得兴高采烈吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.11,0:02:15.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兴高采烈？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.71,0:02:20.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 这么说起来...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.33,0:02:22.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.94,0:02:29.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 今天先发表已经迫在眉睫的期末考试时间安排
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.62,0:02:30.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,期末...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.55,0:02:31.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,考试...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.02,0:02:40.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么晚了是谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.17,0:02:44.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,禀君 禀君 大事不妙了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.56,0:02:47.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,禀君 在考试中要是开什么「红灯」的话
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.09,0:02:50.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就会失去整个暑假是真的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.66,0:02:54.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说是会被带去参加什么叫补习的仪式
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.08,0:02:56.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每天都会被关在学校里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.02,0:02:58.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.51,0:03:00.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的确是要参加补习啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.47,0:03:02.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是真的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.78,0:03:10.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难得这个暑假想好好享受一下天伦之乐的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.40,0:03:16.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会错的 这是对我们神族的挑战
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.91,0:03:20.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事已至此 索性就把学校连同这个世界一起消...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.33,0:03:23.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 你干什么啊 爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.06,0:03:28.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉啊 老爸总是那么吵闹
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.68,0:03:30.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 我们回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.23,0:03:32.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 希娅
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.27,0:03:37.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的没事的 船到桥头自然直
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.38,0:03:42.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是这样做 那边是那样做
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.35,0:03:46.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绿叶少爷倒是很从容呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.83,0:03:47.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别看这家伙那样子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.79,0:03:51.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实可是和琳还有枫一样属于成绩优秀集团的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.09,0:03:54.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真令人气愤 太不公平了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.27,0:04:10.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过话说回来 这是吹的什么风啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.14,0:04:10.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.05,0:04:14.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,禀君居然和我一起学习什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.10,0:04:18.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毕竟希娅的成绩关系到人界的存亡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.71,0:04:20.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希娅每开一次红灯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.29,0:04:23.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人类就要面临一次灭亡可受不了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.43,0:04:27.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸的话说不定真的会干出来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.63,0:04:31.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以的话 倒是该让学习更好的人来教你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.31,0:04:36.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过么 我想两个傻瓜在一起也应该胜过孤军奋战吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.51,0:04:38.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,禀君
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.28,0:04:41.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 快点开始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.58,0:04:42.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.44,0:04:45.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说 禀君
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.99,0:04:48.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个要怎么译好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.19,0:04:54.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个是充当副词作用的to的不定式什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.62,0:04:57.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是...简单来说就是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.93,0:05:05.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这种时候才需要用到字典
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.06,0:05:07.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希娅 拿字典来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.16,0:05:08.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.56,0:05:10.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给 禀君
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.21,0:05:10.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.38,0:05:14.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有了有了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.71,0:05:16.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.17,0:05:18.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看 这里
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.73,0:05:31.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 怎么说好...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.80,0:05:38.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是第一次呢 像这样...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.04,0:05:41.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和禀君两个人独处
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.03,0:05:44.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好不容易到了这里
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.09,0:05:47.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直以来都没有两人独处的机会
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.01,0:05:52.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和禀君在一起 就是日常的景色也会变得不同
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.23,0:05:56.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 八年前初遇的时候也是...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.65,0:06:06.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 为什么哭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.69,0:06:12.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别在那种地方哭 我们走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.11,0:06:39.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 所有人停笔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.61,0:06:41.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把试卷传上来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.02,0:06:53.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,禀君 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.27,0:06:57.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就住在隔壁嘛 不用介意的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.23,0:07:00.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毕竟...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.16,0:07:04.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕 都湿了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.44,0:07:08.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 这个啊 一把伞两个人撑
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.23,0:07:11.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,淋到点雨是正常的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.61,0:07:12.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.39,0:07:14.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.55,0:07:17.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么...只是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.65,0:07:18.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.25,0:07:23.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是...觉得禀君好温柔啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.66,0:07:26.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 一般吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.37,0:07:28.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 很温柔哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.75,0:07:30.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.65,0:07:35.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 禀君
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.08,0:07:37.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点过来嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.20,0:08:05.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,禀君的这一点啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.02,0:08:11.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和琳就是喜欢上了禀君的这一点
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.15,0:08:15.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的话禀君也不会淋到雨了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.92,0:08:17.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希娅...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.26,0:08:21.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下雨真好呢 禀君
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.52,0:08:43.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,禀君 早上了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.18,0:08:46.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,禀君
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.66,0:08:53.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再让我睡一会嘛 难得暑假 枫
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.92,0:08:56.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是枫
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.51,0:08:59.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,禀君 我们约会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.12,0:09:03.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,约会？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.47,0:09:09.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 去哪好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.12,0:09:13.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,禀君 你有什么想去的地方吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.49,0:09:19.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是哦 如果知道要出去的话 倒是会考虑一些
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.80,0:09:23.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的话 由我来主导可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.82,0:09:25.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 交给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.41,0:09:26.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.38,0:09:30.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天要用通宵计划出来的完美约会计划
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.67,0:09:33.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉近和禀君之间的关系
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.81,0:09:36.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光是做好朋友可是不够的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.74,0:09:41.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,禀君 我们去那边看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.92,0:09:43.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 小型卡拉OK
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.02,0:09:45.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起来个二重唱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.69,0:09:49.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和禀君在密室里独处 心跳的好快
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.58,0:09:53.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻烦你 两位高中生
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.84,0:09:57.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有很激烈的家伙在呢...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.61,0:10:00.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这声音 似乎哪里听过
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.10,0:10:06.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,客人们 能麻烦你们轻一点吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.51,0:10:11.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊 我的声音怎么不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.29,0:10:13.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻弓？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.91,0:10:16.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,土见君和希娅
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.64,0:10:21.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听我说哦 这位工作人员说我的歌...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.32,0:10:24.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道就你们两个？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.15,0:10:26.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说的话 土见君
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.76,0:10:29.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和希娅在约会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.81,0:10:32.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们快逃 希娅
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.67,0:10:35.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和禀君难得的二重唱机会
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.06,0:10:38.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,估衣铺？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.11,0:10:42.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 有件衣服我想看看
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.04,0:10:43.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看看...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.85,0:10:48.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,禀君 这件怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.35,0:10:50.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我觉得挺适合你的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.11,0:10:53.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗 那么禀君也 给
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.21,0:10:55.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情侣装？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.86,0:10:59.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然也很适合禀君
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.87,0:11:02.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是...是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.87,0:11:08.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊 你们的关系已经发展到这个地步了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.36,0:11:09.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,树
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.94,0:11:12.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的手脚到很快嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.47,0:11:14.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.66,0:11:17.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心吧 禀
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.58,0:11:21.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会负起责任接收枫和小奈莉奈的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.55,0:11:22.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可不行哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.10,0:11:24.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 小琳
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.40,0:11:26.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是对禀大人一心一意的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.16,0:11:29.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希娅 今天是约会吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.94,0:11:31.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 嗯...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.60,0:11:37.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.92,0:11:38.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.61,0:11:40.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们去下一个地方吧 禀君
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.56,0:11:51.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,禀君不喜欢喝甜的饮料吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.82,0:11:55.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该不喜欢吧 毕竟是男孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.33,0:11:56.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 倒不讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.09,0:12:03.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那...那 禀君愿意的话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.31,0:12:05.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我一起喝这个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.53,0:12:16.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.21,0:12:19.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.80,0:12:25.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 一起喝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.27,0:12:30.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 我要点餐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.22,0:12:34.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎光临
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.53,0:12:37.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡...卡蕾瓦学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.21,0:12:40.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们两位 难道是在约会吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.21,0:12:44.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.01,0:12:48.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,禀和希娅大人lovelove热带果汁
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.75,0:12:52.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两个人一起chu~~吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.01,0:12:58.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这样顺其自然 直接chu~一下什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.69,0:13:00.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.28,0:13:03.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神经...搭错了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.16,0:13:07.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 还是点一般的饮料算了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.39,0:13:09.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.55,0:13:15.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来去哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.44,0:13:16.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保密
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.70,0:13:24.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.74,0:13:26.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.23,0:13:29.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走散了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.15,0:13:35.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样 看的到妈妈吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.10,0:13:37.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不在
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.98,0:13:39.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是这边？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.80,0:13:46.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们走
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.25,0:13:50.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再来一次
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.17,0:13:52.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 再来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.54,0:13:59.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大哥哥快点啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.48,0:14:00.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在就过去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.24,0:14:15.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是喜欢那样的禀君啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.63,0:14:16.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.34,0:14:18.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们走 希娅
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.01,0:14:21.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 我现在就过去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.77,0:14:23.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次和姐姐一起滑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.28,0:14:27.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真砂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.73,0:14:28.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.51,0:14:31.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 真砂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.90,0:14:32.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.16,0:14:34.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.69,0:14:42.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到家了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.71,0:14:46.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天多谢你了 禀君
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.40,0:14:47.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陪了我一天
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.62,0:14:49.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用谢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.05,0:14:53.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然还是不行哦 突发奇想就去邀请你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.56,0:14:57.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一次我会加油的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.41,0:15:02.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用下一次
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.95,0:15:08.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再一起待一会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.68,0:15:11.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.61,0:15:23.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚上的教室实在不同寻常呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.84,0:15:26.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月亮好美
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.41,0:15:29.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里最安静了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.69,0:15:32.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明总是最热闹的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.04,0:15:39.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天玩的很高兴呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.95,0:15:41.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生了许多事情
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.60,0:15:45.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.78,0:16:15.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去海水浴的时候和大家失散 和禀君独处的我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.93,0:16:18.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迷了路以为没法回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.32,0:16:24.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,禀君一直保护着这样胆怯的我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.82,0:16:28.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实在很温柔呢 越来越喜欢他了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.98,0:16:35.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然暗暗期待着 不过两个人看来离恋人还是有段距离
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.24,0:16:39.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明如此爸爸他却又误会了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.43,0:16:42.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自说自话的就说我们要结婚
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.83,0:16:52.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,禀君 那个很有趣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.03,0:16:53.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.09,0:16:53.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说结婚了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.73,0:16:56.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是般配呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.22,0:16:57.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,年轻真好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.14,0:16:59.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会吧...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.48,0:17:01.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该不会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.37,0:17:04.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过总觉得一直被盯着看
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.38,0:17:04.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 看他们
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.03,0:17:07.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说是要结婚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.80,0:17:09.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真令人羡慕
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.71,0:17:18.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了 发现土见君了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.76,0:17:22.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 土见君 希娅
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.42,0:17:23.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干嘛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.14,0:17:25.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出什么事了 麻弓
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.96,0:17:30.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还问什么事 那么就赶快
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.19,0:17:34.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,土见君 请说说现在的心境
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.27,0:17:36.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使你做出这次抉择的契机是？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.06,0:17:37.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.28,0:17:40.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来的事就交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.57,0:17:45.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,枫和奈莉奈就由本公子来接收了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.10,0:17:49.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们到底在说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.49,0:17:51.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在不是炒得很火嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.42,0:17:55.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能成为神也能成为恶魔的男人选择的是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.05,0:17:57.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是 神
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.78,0:17:59.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们不是要结婚吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.28,0:18:02.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.01,0:18:08.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么会变成这样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.86,0:18:11.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和禀君要结婚
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.45,0:18:14.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 希娅 连你都胡说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.32,0:18:27.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唔 豆腐和大葱还有瘦肉和魔芋丝以及...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.21,0:18:28.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.53,0:18:37.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于见了面 更喜欢禀大人了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.08,0:18:42.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是...这也已经
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.47,0:18:45.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使这样也...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.62,0:18:56.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还是喜欢禀大人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.67,0:19:06.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琳
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.17,0:19:27.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.22,0:19:33.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就一定要背负其他喜欢那个人的人的心意吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.54,0:19:40.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样下去果然不行
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.30,0:19:43.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是要怎么做...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.33,0:20:03.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.56,0:20:21.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 突然把你带到这种地方来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.52,0:20:25.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我也有话要对希娅说
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.91,0:20:30.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实我...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.60,0:20:35.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.26,0:20:40.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我啊 听说要和禀君结婚的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.98,0:20:46.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望大家都能认同我是配得上做禀君妻子的人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.44,0:20:56.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琳和小枫 还有...还有
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.25,0:20:59.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之 想让世界上所有的人认同
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.83,0:21:04.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是现在的我还差远了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.11,0:21:10.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只知道考虑自己 也给禀君添了麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.62,0:21:12.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希娅...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.98,0:21:18.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我会比现在更喜欢禀君
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.50,0:21:23.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也让禀君更加了解我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.15,0:21:31.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后如果禀君能从全世界喜欢禀君的人中选中我的话...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.05,0:21:32.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.98,0:21:38.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是哦
